  "S02bsu004_u:207": "śṛṃgiriṭinandikeśvarakārttikeyacandrasūryagaṇapatisahāyakṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:208": "nagnaśravaṇakṛtaṃ {nagnaśramaṇakṛtaṃ} vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:209": "arhatakṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
