  "S02bsu004_u:212": "vajrapāṇi guhyakādhipatikṛtāṃ vidyāṃ cīndayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:213": "yatra yatrakṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:214": "yena kāritāṃ tasya kṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:215": "muṇḍaśravaṇakṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:216": "dūtadūtīceṭacetīkṛtāṃ vidyāṃ",
  "S02bsu004_u:217": "chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:218": "sarvarṣivarakṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:219": "sarvadevatagaṇakṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:220": "sarvāhitaiṣipatikṛtāṃ vidyāṃ chindayāmyasinā kīlayāmi vajreṇa /",
  "S02bsu004_u:221": "om bhagavati rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca sarvabhayebhyaḥ sarvopadravopasargopāyāsebhyaḥ sarvaduṣṭapraduṣṭān sarvapratyamitrāhitaiṣiṇo vā tathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre namostu te /",
  "S02bsu004_u:222": "sarvabuddhanamaskṛte /",
