  "S02bsu004_u:426": "sarvajvarāḥ śirovartimapanayantu mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca arddhāvabhedakam,",
  "S02bsu004_u:427_0": "arocakam akṣirogaṃ nāsarogaṃ mukharogaṃ kaṇṭharogaṃ hṛdrogaṃ galagrahaṃ karṇaśūlaṃ",
  "S02bsu004_u:427_1": "dantaśūlam uraḥśūlaṃ hṛdayaśūlaṃ marmaśūlaṃ pṛṣṭhaśūlam udaraśūlaṃ vastiśūlaṃ gudaśūlaṃ",
  "S02bsu004_u:427_2": "yoniśūlaṃ pradaraśūlam ūrūśūlaṃ jaṅghāśūlaṃ hastaśūlaṃ pādaśūlam aṅgapratyaṅgaśūlaṃ mama cāpanayantu /",
  "S02bsu004_u:428_0": "bhūtapretavetālaḍākinījvaradagdhakaṇḍūkiṭībhakuṣṭapittakaplīhabhagaṃdaralūtāpāmāvaisarpalohaliṅgāśeṣaśvāsatrāsakāsamūrchāgaraviṣayayogāgnyudakamāramārīkalahavairakāntārākālamṛtyutryambukatrailāṭakavṛścikasarpanakulasiṃhavyāghrarkṣatarakṣucarmaramakaravṛkataskarājīvakāyikānapanayantu",
  "S02bsu004_u:428_1": "{Śambuka(tai)lāṭaŚ} /",
  "S02bsu004_u:429_0": "anyeṣāṃ sarveṣāṃ sitātapatramahoṣṇīṣamahāpratyaṅgirāvidyānubhāvena yāvad dvādaśayojanābhyantareṇa",
  "S02bsu004_u:429_1": "pañcāśatayojanābhyantareṇa vā vidyābandhaṃ karomi tejobandhanaṃ karomi sarvavidyābandhanaṃ",
  "S02bsu004_u:429_2": "karomi paravidyābandhanaṃ karomi sīmābandhanaṃ karomi dharaṇībandhanaṃ karomi daśadigbandhanaṃ",
  "S02bsu004_u:429_3": "karomi parasainyastambhanaṃ karomi /",
  "S02bsu004_u:430": "tadyathā om anane 2 khakhane 2 vīṣama 2 vīre 2 maunya 2 śānte 2 dānte 2 vajradhara bandhabandhani vajrapāṇe phaṭ /",
  "S02bsu004_u:431": "om hūṃ ṣṭroṃ phaṭ 2 svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:432": "om vajrapāśe bandha 2 vajrapāśaṃ ca sarvaduṣṭavighnavināyakān hūṃ phaṭ 2 rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:433_0": "ya imāṃ sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāpratyaṅgirāmahāvidyārājñīṃ likhitvā",
  "S02bsu004_u:433_1": "bhūrjapatre vastre vā valkale vā kāyagataṃ vā kaṇṭhagataṃ vā kṛtvā dhārayiṣyati vāciṣyati",
  "S02bsu004_u:433_2": "aśuddhakaṃ na kṣamiṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:434": "sarvakṛtyakarma na kramiṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:435": "nagaraṃ kramiṣyati,",
  "S02bsu004_u:436": "yogaṃ kramiṣyati,",
  "S02bsu004_u:437": "nākālamṛtyunā kālaṃ kariṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:438": "sarvagrahāṇāṃ sarvavighnavināyakānāṃ ca priyo bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:439_0": "manaāpaścaturaśītikalpakoṭīsahasrāṇi jātau jātau jātismaro bhaviṣyati caturaśītivajrakulakoṭiniyutaśatasahasrāṇi",
  "S02bsu004_u:439_1": "vidyādevatā nityaṃ satatasamitaṃ tasya rakṣāvaraṇaguptiṃ kariṣyanti /",
  "S02bsu004_u:440": "caturaśītivajradūtī kiṃkarā nityaṃ paripālayiṣyanti teṣāmapi priyo bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:441": "manaāpaśca na kadācidyakṣatvaṃ na rākṣasatvaṃ na bhūtatvaṃ na piśācatvaṃ na pūtanatvaṃ na kaṭapūtanatvaṃ na manuṣyadāridryaṃ pratyanubhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:442": "gaṅgānadībālukāsaṃkhyeyāprameyāṇāṃ buddhānāṃ bhagavatāṃ puṇyaskandhena samanvāgato bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:443": "imāṃ ca sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ mahavidyārājñīṃ dhārayamāṇa abrahmacārī brahmacārī bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:444": "amaunī maunī bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:445": "aśuciḥ śucirbhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:446": "anupavāsī upavāsī bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:447": "yo 'pi pañcānantaryakārī syāt so 'pi [Sitā_154] nirdhūtapāpo bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:448": "pūrvakarmāvaraṇaṃ niravaśeṣaṃ parikṣayaṃ gacchati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:449": "yaḥ kaścit mātṛgrāme tathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitā mahāpratyaṅgirā mahāvidyārājñīṃ dhārayamāṇaḥ putrārthī putraṃ pratilabhate /",
  "S02bsu004_u:450": "āyuḥpuṇyabalaṃ pratilabhate /",
  "S02bsu004_u:451": "itaścyutvā sukhavatyāṃ lokadhātāvupapadyate /",
  "S02bsu004_u:452": "sa ca rāgadveṣamohamānadarpavigato bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:453_0": "yaḥ kaścinmanuṣyamāre paśumāre gomāre sarve 'pyupadravopasargopāyāsaparacakrāgamaneṣu",
  "S02bsu004_u:453_1": "tasya bhagavato jinasya samyaksaṃbuddhasya sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāṃ",
  "S02bsu004_u:453_2": "dhvajāgrāvaropitāṃ kṛtvā mahatā pūjāsatkāreṇa mahatīṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā sarvanagaradvāreṣu",
  "S02bsu004_u:453_3": "praveśayet vihāre vā grāme vā nagare vā janapade vā nigame vā śmaśāne vā parvate",
  "S02bsu004_u:453_4": "vā araṇyāyatane vā imāmaparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ vidyārājñīṃ mahatā satkāreṇa praveśayet /",
  "S02bsu004_u:454": "praveśitamātreṇa praśāntikṛto bhaviṣyati /",
  "S02bsu004_u:455": "sarve 'pyupadravopasargopāyāsāḥ paracakrāṇi praśāmyanti /",
  "S02bsu004_u:456": "ananto nāgarājā śaṅkhapālo nāgarājā mahākṛṣṇo nāgarājā nandyupanaṃdau nāgarājānau anye ca sarve te nāgarājānaḥ kāle ca kālaṃ varṣayiṣyanti kālena kālaṃ autsukyamāpatsyate /",
  "S02bsu004_u:457": "kālena kālaṃ garjayiṣyanti sarvarogopadravāṃścopaśamayiṣyanti /",
  "S02bsu004_u:458": "om ṣṭroṃ bandha 2 sarvaduṣṭān rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:459": "om hūṃ ṣṭroṃ bandha 2 duṣṭān rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca vajrapāṇe hūṃ phaṭ svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:460": "om sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣa avalokitamūrdhni tejorāśi /",
  "S02bsu004_u:461": "om jvala 2 dhak 2 khāda 2 dara 2 vidara 2 chinte {chinda} 2 bhinda 2 hūṃ 2 phaṭ 3 rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:462": "om sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre hūṃ phaṭ /",
  "S02bsu004_u:463": "om rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca hūṃ phaṭ svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:464": "tadyathā - om anale 2 acare 2 khasame 2 vīre 2 saumye 2 sarvabuddhādhiṣṭhānādhiṣṭhite sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre sarvaduṣṭacittān hūṃ phaṭ svāhā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:465": "buddhayogena sarvopadraveṣu trijaptā kartavyā /",
  "S02bsu004_u:466": "sarvabuddhabodhisattvāśca sadevamānuṣāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragaśca loko bhagavato bhāṣitamabhyanandanniti /",
  "S02bsu004_u:467": "āryasarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmaparājitā pratyaṅgirā mahāvidyārājñī samāptā //"
}